name: Aaron Community Cultural Center
review_text: Very clean and organized. Workers are very polite and helpful.

name: Aaron Community Cultural Center
review_text: This organization is a gift to the community.  During  my visit, I saw an individual ride up and helped themselves to about 3 items from the community refrigerator for homeless or others who are experiencing food deprivation.  This gives them a place to go and is just one of the many services this center provides.
